{"tid":789072,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"(終於有片) 網上瘋傳空姐解衣露酥胸！鏡頭前「脫黑絲襪＋嗅聞」","createTime":"2018-08-22T03:31:09.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-22T14:38:47.000Z","uid":184679,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"9db80452a37f460bbd3681847564e18ba6f5edc4","tid":789072,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-22T03:31:09.000Z","msg":"近日英國航空（British Airways）一名空姐被爆料拍攝情色風格的影片，目的疑似是為了拍賣貼身黑絲襪和鞋子，不僅在影片中脫下原味黑絲襪聞，還在鏡頭前脫衣露胸，影片也在網上瘋傳。<br />\n<br />\n據外媒報導，一該名空服員在鏡頭前說：「我希望你們都能聞到這個味道。」並直接脫下她的原味黑絲襪，放到鼻前嗅聞，甚至脫下黑色高跟鞋，表示她在沒有穿內褲的情況下，穿了這組黑絲襪與高跟鞋一天，疑似就是為了賣出去。<br />\n<br />\n據了解，目前該名空姐已遭停職，英國航空發言人也表示，公司對於員工採取高標準，也希望員工能對自己的行為負責。報導提到，其實這種空姐穿過的「配備」，在網拍上很熱門，先前就曾有XL尺寸的原味黑絲襪，一度喊價到75英鎊。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hottopic.chinatimes.com/20180822001497-260803\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhottopic.chinatimes.com%2F20180822001497-260803&d=PHxlR1nZkxZlRZVXiLssDU%2FDJpISyAq9ELy6OyFxwDc%3D&h=2e6b40ac\" target=\"_blank\">http://hottopic.chinatimes.com/20180822001497-260803</a>"},{"pid":"f1f8fa202f258b8f03bbf706bb73be3f4c31263b","tid":789072,"uid":40272,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-22T03:32:57.000Z","msg":"我都好想聞 有無原片<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"518f607e53e2ca209fae1160ba837b7caf08e644","tid":789072,"uid":21423,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-22T03:33:02.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"d029b5cbf06a8fc2899a7c2667da69a9b49c12bc","tid":789072,"uid":3241,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-22T03:33:38.000Z","msg":"呢d連登永遠都冇片"},{"pid":"0d1c30380d19a5d7a60428e2b8d27c7306365d24","tid":789072,"uid":137604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-22T03:34:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"93c839de6b37ea1